{"tid":505351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男護理員涉4度性侵男院友 裁判官邊看案情邊搖頭","createTime":"2017-12-21T04:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T05:48:01.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4b9150e75ed0bfada89bc42eb79998b5214b94","tid":505351,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"於東華三院轄下一間護理院工作的男護理員，涉於今年7至11月期間4度非禮院內同一名男院友。男護理員被控今提堂，被告暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至下月25日再訊，以讓控方取得法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n被告徐頌軒(25歲)，被控4項非禮罪，指他於今年7月、9至11月非禮同一名男院友。裁判官看罷控方所呈交的案情後搖頭，指被告於工作地方犯案，問控罪是否適合，又問被告是否仍在護理院工作，被告表示現已離職。<br />\n<br />\n被告最後獲准以3,000元保釋候訊，但期間不得接觸6名控方證人，並且不得進入案發地點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57608817?_ga=2.81104468.234410376.1513818443-1014210623.1513818443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608817%3F_ga%3D2.81104468.234410376.1513818443-1014210623.1513818443&d=pLN3bEDIYDO9G7KjYHSZG%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ba18d7f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608817%3F_ga%3D2.81104468.234410376.1513818443-1014210623.1513818443&h=077a3a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57608817?_ga=2.81104468.234410376.1513818443-1014210623.1513818443</a>"},{"pid":"af479319456ba3aaba332f4b75d86731471affb1","tid":505351,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"HEHE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcc2d93d4297f5e047253af62088d06e7ff5849","tid":505351,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e472c24ae4a8abfe7673796f5b8130e573c531